********************************************************************************

Automated install is complete. There are a few steps that need to be completed
manually.

 1) Launch dropbox and login - get the sync started
 2) Change the launch key for Alfred to CTRL-SPACE
 3) System Preferences -> Security & Privacy -> Privacy, enable Keyboard Maestro,
    Synergy, Hammerspoon, Karabiner, Alfred, CheatSheet, DropBox
 4) Launch 1Password & set up sync
 5) Launch Chrome, login, let it link to 1Password, install pinboard plugin
 6) Launch Safari, let it link to 1Password, install pinboard plugin
 7) Login to Spotify
 8) Install Alfred Powerpack

* setup favorites in finder
    + Home
    - All My Files
* add applications folder to dock, set to view as folder
* set downloads to display as folder in dock
* set up slack teams (757dev, codeforva)
